name: Cherry Dash
overview: Released at Visionparty 2002 and also in GO64! 2002/10. "I suppose I really should have called this game "Snodge's Bad Day", but well, this came before SBD. Run across the bridge, collecting cherries, but don't get squished by the falling boulders, it might hurt a bit. (Ouch! That gotta hurt)" ~Richard Bayliss
